methods.name: public Builder setAdsSdkName(@NonNull String adsSdkName)
methods.comment:
* Set Ads Sdk Name. * *

This must be called by SDKs running outside of the Sandbox. Other clients must not * call it. * * @param adsSdkName the Ads Sdk Name.

methods.name: public Builder setShouldRecordObservation(boolean recordObservation)
methods.comment:
* Set the Record Observation.
         *
         * @param recordObservation whether to record that the caller has observed the topics of the
         *     host app or not. This will be used to determine if the caller can receive the topic
         *     in the next epoch.
